005" rel="cite" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131">Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 (S.I. 2005/3131)</a>, <a class="LegCitation" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131/regulation/1/3" title="Go to Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 regs. 1(3)" rel="cite">regs. 1(3)</a>, <a class="LegCitation" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131/regulation/8/2" title="Go to Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 8(2)" rel="cite"><strong>8(2)</strong></a></span></p></div><div class="LegCommentaryItem" id="commentary-key-65ed18f5fec03834336e8b331a9ac4af"><p class="LegCommentaryPara"><span class="LegCommentaryType"><a href="#reference-key-65ed18f5fec03834336e8b331a9ac4af" title="Go back to reference for this commentary item">F41</a></span><span class="LegCommentaryText">Words in reg. 7(1) inserted (5.12.2005) by <a class="LegCitation" title="Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005" rel="cite" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131">Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 (S.I. 2005/3131)</a>, <a class="LegCitation" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131/regulation/1/2" title="Go to Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 regs. 1(2)" rel="cite">regs. 1(2)</a>, <a class="LegCitation" href="/id/uksi/2005/3131/regulation/6/2" title="Go to Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2005 6(2)" rel="cite"><strong>6(2)</strong></a></span></p></div><div class="LegCommentaryItem" id="commentary-key-811dcf2d71d6cdea603b989f2380cf06"><p class="LegCommentaryPara"><span class="LegCommentaryType"><a href="#reference-key-811dcf2d71d6cdea603b989f2380cf06" title="Go back to reference for this commentary item">F42</a></span><span class="LegCommentaryText">Word in reg. 7(1)(a) substituted (6.4.2002) by <a class="LegCitation" title="Social Security Contributions (Intermediaries) (Amendment) Regulations 2002" rel="ci